comment._content: C. Sugden, Tobacconist and Hairdresser. See signage on wall of building visible in this photo of the wider streetscape: [http://www.flickr.com/photos/state-records-nsw/9388956666/] Location is Parramatta Rd, Five Dock (between Ashfield and Drummoyne), near Croydon Rd. - trove.nla.gov.au/ndp/del/article/16324247 [see "Businesses for sale", 1st column]. Sugden was still there in May 1932 - trove.nla.gov.au/ndp/del/article/46653218
